{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-generic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-5","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"assignments":[],"bilibiliIds":null,"block":"learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities","challengeType":19,"description":"","nodules":null,"explanation":"<section id=\"explanation\">\n<p>Kada vas neko pita <strong>pitanje da/ne</strong>, često možete odgovoriti sa kratkim odgovorom. Ovo se takođe primenjuje na pitanja u kontekstu <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Present Perfect</span>.</p>\n<p>Za kratak odgovor, koristite <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Yes</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">No</span>, praćen karakterom (kao što su <span class=\"highlighted-text\">I</span>, <span class=\"highlighted-text\">we</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">they</span>) zatim <span class=\"highlighted-text\">have</span> ili <span class=\"highlighted-text\">haven't</span>. Na primer, za pitanje <span class=\"highlighted-text\">Have you seen the report?</span> možete koristiti kratke odgovore:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Yes, I have.</span>, ili</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">No, I haven't.</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Ovo čini vaš odgovor jasnim i kratkim bez ponavljanja celog pitanja.</p>\n</section>","helpCategory":"English","instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Slušajte audio odgovor na pitanje ispod.</p>\n</section>","fields":{"slug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-how-to-talk-about-past-activities/task-5"},"questions":[{"text":"<p>Linda je pročitala te izveštaje. Koji izbor je najbolji odgovor?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Yes, I have.</span></p>","feedback":null,"audioId":"EN885f75b0"},{"answer":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Yes, I do.</span></p>","feedback":"<p><span class=\"highlighted-text\">Do</span> koristi se za odgovaranje na pitanja